IFS=$'\n'
echo "<?xml version='1.0'?><items>" for line in $(grep --extended-regexp '\[.+\]\(.+\)' < "$mdfile"); do sed -E "s|.*\[(.+)\]\((.+)\).*|<item arg='\2' valid='yes'><title>\1</title></item>|" <<< "${line}" done echo "</items>"

Quick extension to Knowledge Map.
Ability to search through :
- all main nodes from Knowledge Map - all nodes from 'more' node from Knowledge Map (books, courses ..) - all imgur albums from 'images' mind map from Knoledge Map
Big thank you to Vitor without whom this workflow wouldn't exist. 💚
